cisco-ai-skill-scanner
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Source:  https://github.com/cisco-ai-defense/skill-scanner
Package: cisco-ai-skill-scanner (PyPI)
License: Apache License, Version 2.0

AIControl invokes this package as an isolated subprocess (never imported
in-process) to run its default deterministic analyzers only — see
app/services/scanners/skill_scanner_adapter.py. The optional LLM/cloud
analysis modes (--use-llm, --use-aidefense, --use-virustotal) are never
enabled by AIControl.

